	</tr>
	<tr>
		<td colspan="2"><hr class="sep" />A basic oscilliscope view is incredibly easy and requires no real calculations.  Just plot a point based directly on the output sample (-32768 = bottom, 0 = center, 32767 = top).  I've done them this way in the past and they look fine.

		

		</td>
	</tr>
